name: Aura and Mare Bella/Bello Fiore (Overlord)
description:
It is a character LoRAs of both Aura and Mare Bella Fiore from Overlord. V1.0 was trained on AbyssOrangeMix2_hard. v1.1 loras were trained on NovelAI model.

I recommend you add:

  • "pointy ears, heterochromia, blonde hair, gloves, short hair, green eyes, blue eyes" and "red shirt, vest, long sleeves, brown gloves, elf, dark skin," for prompts with Aura.

  • "otoko no ko, pointy ears, heterochromia, blond hair, blue eyes, green eyes, dark skin" and "skirt, zettai ryouiki, crossdressing" for prompts with Mare.

modelVersions.name: v1.1 (Aura)
modelVersions.description:
Separated model in two loras. The previous idea of two characters in one lora wasn't fine.

Retrained the models with larger dataset on NovelAI model following this guide: https://civitai.com/models/22530/guide-make-your-own-loras-easy-and-free
